8
0:0:25,287 --> 0:0:29,287
Your long-term job status will
be decided at the board meeting.


9
0:0:29,287 --> 0:0:33,447
Until then, and l cannot bend on this,


10
0:0:33,447 --> 0:0:36,327
l don't want you
setting foot on the premises.


11
0:0:36,327 --> 0:0:40,527
- l'm going to be here all day.
