<i>that the average intern</i>


23
0:1:29,727 --> 0:1:33,287
<i>has to disimpact 1 5 to 20 bowels a week,</i>


24
0:1:33,287 --> 0:1:36,687
<i>There's an oath among interns</i>
<i>never to make fun of each other</i>


25
0:1:36,687 --> 0:1:39,47
<i>for doing the things we have to do,</i>


26
0:1:39,47 --> 0:1:41,727
You have to touch someone's hiney.


27
0:1:41,727 --> 0:1:44,767
Dorian, come with me. And Dr...


28
0:1:44,767 --> 0:1:46,327
- Reid.
- Sure. Why not?


29
0:1:46,327 --> 0:1:49,727
Take over for him.


30
0:1:49,727 --> 0:1:51,767
l'm assigning you to a board member


31
0:1:51,767 --> 0:1:54,887
